== 製作 ==
=== 拍攝 ===
正式拍攝於2015年10月19日在[[捷克|捷克]]的首都[[布拉格|布拉格]]開始進行，在那拍攝了約十週<ref name="Oct2015CS">{{cite news|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/623737-underworld-5-begins-shooting-with-kate-beckinsale-and-theo-james|title=''Underworld 5'' Begins Shooting with Kate Beckinsale and Theo James|date=2015-10-19|publisher=comingsoon.net|last1=Evry|first1=Max|accessdate=2015-10-20|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020153334/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/623737-underworld-5-begins-shooting-with-kate-beckinsale-and-theo-james|dead-url=no}}</ref>。劇組成員包括攝影師{{link-en|卡爾·華特·林登勞|Karl Walter Lindenlaub}}、美術指導昂德烈·那瓦西爾、服裝設計寶珍娜·尼基京斯基和剪輯彼得·阿蒙森<ref name="Oct2015CS" />。攝製於2015年12月11日結束，並接著開始進入後製<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-121115-james-franco-and-seth-rogen-start-the-disaster-artist-owen-wilson-ed-helms-wrap-bastards/|title=On the Set 12/11/15: James Franco and Seth Rogen Start ‘The Disaster Artist’, Owen Wilson & Ed Helms Wrap ‘Bastards’|date=2015-12-11|work=ssninsider.com|accessdate=2015-12-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213213620/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-121115-james-franco-and-seth-rogen-start-the-disaster-artist-owen-wilson-ed-helms-wrap-bastards/|archivedate=2015年12月13日}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
電影最初定於2016年10月21日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/sony-films-bad-boys-jennifer-lawrence-passengers-1201557242/|title=Sony Dates 16 Films Including Two More 'Bad Boys' Sequels, 'Jumanji' Remake|date=2015-08-05|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|last=Kroll|first=Justin|accessdate=2015-09-21|archive-date=2017-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623194610/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/sony-films-bad-boys-jennifer-lawrence-passengers-1201557242/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來改至2017年1月6日上映<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/underworld_blood_wars_2017/|title=Rotten Tomatoes|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011061015/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/underworld_blood_wars_2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而臺灣和香港則搶先於2016年12月1日上映。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅19%，基於36條評論，平均分為4/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/underworld_blood_wars_2017 |title=Underworld: Blood Wars (2016) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-12-02 |archive-date=2019-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523142734/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/underworld_blood_wars_2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分20，評價不佳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/underworld-blood-wars|title=Underworld: Blood Wars reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-12-07|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629064307/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/underworld-blood-wars|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[IMDB|IMDB]]評分為6.4/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3717252 |title=Underworld: Blood Wars (2016) |work=[IMDb] |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archive-date=2021-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110232641/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3717252/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
在美國，《決戰異世界：弒血之戰》與《[[關鍵少數|關鍵少數]]》、《[[漫漫回家路_(2016年電影)|漫漫回家路]]》、《[[怪物來敲門|怪物來敲門]]》共同競爭，估計首週末能從三千零七十間戲院中獲得1500萬至1900萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-20170103-story.html |title='Hidden Figures' is likely to draw crowds as 'Rogue One' stays on top of the box office |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=2017-01-06 |archive-date=2018-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702235354/http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-20170103-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首週末票房僅1310萬美元，位居當週第四，同時也是該系列最低的成績<ref name="opening">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/rogue-one-hidden-figures-underworld-blood-wars-weekend-box-office-1201879773/ |title=‘Rogue One’ Doesn’t Want To Fall To ‘Hidden Figures’ As Winter Storm Helena Closes Theaters |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2017-01-09 |archive-date=2019-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418180445/https://deadline.com/2017/01/rogue-one-hidden-figures-underworld-blood-wars-weekend-box-office-1201879773/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在臺灣，北市首週末票房收入為659萬新臺幣，位居當週第三名。

